column5: I sae the thread about Brad Paisley's song so I decidede to share my fave fishing song. It sounds alot like Carrie Underwood's Jesus take the wheel. LOL Tim Hawkins is a funny dude.  THis may have been posted before but I still laugh everytime I watch it.   Upper thigh injury is a classic.

While I am at it I might as well post his classic "Things you don't say to your wife".  He still mentions hunting and fishing so this might be my second favourite fishing song. lol   If you have never heard this song, listen to it.  Short and sweet.
http://www.evtv1.com/player.aspx?itemnum=15328  i should get all these on a disc.
This should get Brian's toes a'tappin'...one of my favorite fishing songs...  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VuoK0ialEY0

Sun and fun, I'm sure that Cletus would fit right into this one..   <iframe title="YouTube video player" class="youtube-player" type="text/html" width="640" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/uI7Ghu1FpnQ" frameborder="0" allowFullScreen></iframe>
Never heard of this guy before some pretty good tunes!
Squid jiggin. Now that'll draw a memory or 2 ta mind. Sitting on the govt wharf in a deep water harbour catching squid in N.S.
Watch it Paul, we have 12 year old daughters watching this.
